---
const title = "Artwork Gallery";
const date = "2025-04-08";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Artwork Gallery</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #0d0f1c;
        color: #c9c7ff;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #b48eff;
        text-shadow: 0 0 2px #b48eff;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #b48eff;
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 #2e254e;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      .prompt {
        color: #888;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }

      a {
        color: #79b8ff;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 1rem;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: #b48eff;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      iframe {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: 1000px;
        border: none;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      hr {
        border: none;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #2e254e, #b48eff, #2e254e);
        opacity: 0.4;
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Artwork & Design</h1>
    <span class="prompt">> Log Date: 2025-04-08</span>
    <p class="excerpt">
      Syrenwork blends analog craftsmanship with digital vision. Explore art, fabrication, and interactive tools developed by Lorelei Noble.
    </p>

    <p>
      Welcome to <strong>Syrenwork</strong> — a journey through the intersection of traditional craftsmanship and contemporary digital expression.
      I'm <strong>Lorelei Noble</strong>, an artist, programmer, and developer. My work spans stained glass, wood and metal sculpture, digital art, and interactive technologies — all designed to inspire transformation and reconnection through emotion, light, and movement.
    </p>

    <p>
      I also provide fabrication and consulting services, from interior components and installations to project development and design systems.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <div>
      <a href="https://www.pictorem.com/gallery/Syrenwork" target="_blank">Prints</a>
      <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/Syrenwork" target="_blank">Shop</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/syrenwork" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
    </div>

    <iframe
      src="https://www.pictorem.com/gallery/Syrenwork"
      allowfullscreen
      sandbox="allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-top-navigation"
    ></iframe>

    <hr />

    <p>
      Want to collaborate or request a custom piece? Contact me through
      <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/Syrenwork" target="_blank">Etsy</a> or explore more at
      <a href="/blog">Arynwood DevLog</a>.
    </p>

    <hr />
  </body>
</html>